  {
    "text": "♪ Mellow instrumental hip-hop ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Mellow instrumental hip-hop ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=3"
  },
  {
    "text": "Howdy! Welcome to ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Enhance your iPad and iPhone apps for the Shared Space.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "My name is John Marc. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm a platform compatibility engineer. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=16"
  },
  {
    "text": "Most iPad and iPhone apps run great without any changes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "taking advantage of the hard work you've already done ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=24"
  },
  {
    "text": "and making it work on Apple's latest platform. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=27"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're just getting started, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=31"
  },
  {
    "text": "watch \"Run your iPad and iPhone apps in the Shared Space\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "first to learn about the system's built-in behaviors, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=37"
  },
  {
    "text": "functional differences, and testing setup. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=40"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this video, I'll go over how to enhance ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "your iPad or iPhone app from a great app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=46"
  },
  {
    "text": "to one that feels at home on this new platform. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=50"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll review the new interaction, visual-appearance changes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=52"
  },
  {
    "text": "and media recording and playback functionality ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=56"
  },
  {
    "text": "your app should expect. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=58"
  },
  {
    "text": "Interaction on this platform is fun and feels familiar. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=61"
  },
  {
    "text": "One of the key components is the new natural input technique. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=65"
  },
  {
    "text": "Tap allows people to look at a button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=70"
  },
  {
    "text": "then tap their fingers together to interact. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "People can tap to toggle, tap, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=75"
  },
  {
    "text": "hold and swipe to interact with a slider, or tap a button.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=77"
  },
  {
    "text": "Direct touch requires reaching out to the app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=84"
  },
  {
    "text": "and touching the button in the space with one finger. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "Regardless of interaction method, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=91"
  },
  {
    "text": "the button provides continuous visual feedback ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=93"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help with interaction accuracy. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=95"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this video, the cursor represents ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=100"
  },
  {
    "text": "where a person is looking. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=102"
  },
  {
    "text": "When looking at a button, a highlight hover effect tints ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "the control's color to help understand where focus is. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=106"
  },
  {
    "text": "Notice that each item highlights ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "while looking through this list. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=112"
  },
  {
    "text": "That highlight follows focus to the left, or right ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=115"
  },
  {
    "text": "so it's clear what's happening. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=119"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hover effects exist on controls ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=122"
  },
  {
    "text": "to inform where people are looking. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=124"
  },
  {
    "text": "Controls that are inactive do not get hover effects. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=127"
  },
  {
    "text": "System controls take care of all these hover effects for you. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=131"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're only using the standard controls, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=135"
  },
  {
    "text": "you're ready to rock and roll without any changes here. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=137"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're building custom controls, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=140"
  },
  {
    "text": "your hover effects may need some tuning. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=142"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's an example of an app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=146"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a card-based interface on iPad. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "Each card contains a photo, title, date, and menu button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=151"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here is that same app running in Simulator. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=157"
  },
  {
    "text": "Because the menu button is a system control, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=160"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's already working as expected. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=162"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, each card is a simple VStack with a .onTap modifier, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=164"
  },
  {
    "text": "so it does not receive hover effects. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "That entire card is a tap target, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=171"
  },
  {
    "text": "so it needs hover effects to inform people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=174"
  },
  {
    "text": "it has an available interaction. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=176"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's focus on one of those cards to fix it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=178"
  },
  {
    "text": "System controls, like Button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=182"
  },
  {
    "text": "receive hover effects automatically, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "so the button used as a menu here already has a hover effect. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, in this example, people click the entire card ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=190"
  },
  {
    "text": "to view more detail. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=192"
  },
  {
    "text": "By adding .hoverEffect onto the VStack, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "the entire card becomes available ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=198"
  },
  {
    "text": "for interaction update and informs people it's tappable. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=200"
  },
  {
    "text": "Many custom video players have optimized hit targets ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=205"
  },
  {
    "text": "so people don't have to be quite so precise ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=208"
  },
  {
    "text": "to interact with them. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=210"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this example of a custom video player on iPad, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "the tap targets are significantly larger ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=215"
  },
  {
    "text": "than the symbols on the skip forward ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=217"
  },
  {
    "text": "and skip backward buttons. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=220"
  },
  {
    "text": "The bordered boxes here show the size of the tap targets ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=222"
  },
  {
    "text": "where people can interact. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "On Simulator now, hover effects ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "highlight those tap targets, which shows a tappable region ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=231"
  },
  {
    "text": "over the entire area. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=234"
  },
  {
    "text": "That same example in the Shared Space ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=236"
  },
  {
    "text": "now shows the hidden attributes with hover effects. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "This change of appearance is exposing the truth ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=242"
  },
  {
    "text": "but does not feel correct.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=245"
  },
  {
    "text": "If we zoom into our example, to keep the existing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=249"
  },
  {
    "text": "tapping behavior with reduced appearance, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=252"
  },
  {
    "text": "add a custom shape to the .contentShape modifiers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=254"
  },
  {
    "text": "By using a custom shape, apps can provide an origin and size ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=258"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the .contentShape modifiers, which will be smaller ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "than the tappable region. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=265"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this video, people looking directly at the button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=269"
  },
  {
    "text": "will see a hover effect. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=272"
  },
  {
    "text": "And with this change, tapping outside the hover effect bounds ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "will match expectations from iPad and iPhone experiences. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=277"
  },
  {
    "text": "Back on the simulator with the full example. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=283"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now with this custom shape, the hover effect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=285"
  },
  {
    "text": "appears on just the buttons ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=288"
  },
  {
    "text": "but allows tapping outside of them. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=290"
  },
  {
    "text": "Excellent! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=292"
  },
  {
    "text": "In most cases, hover effects on system controls work great; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=294"
  },
  {
    "text": "however, the ability to customize hover effects ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=299"
  },
  {
    "text": "is powerful. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=301"
  },
  {
    "text": "With the new hover effect API, apps can create hover effects ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "for custom buttons, custom shapes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=306"
  },
  {
    "text": "or even opt out of a control if necessary. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=309"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's inspect how to do that. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": ".buttonStyle is a great way to consistently apply ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=314"
  },
  {
    "text": "a custom style to all buttons in apps. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=317"
  },
  {
    "text": "When applying custom styling, it turns off hover effects. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "To reenable hover effects on a custom .buttonStyle button, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "add the .hoverEffect() modifier to app elements. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=328"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here is my simple button with a custom button style. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=332"
  },
  {
    "text": "Looking at the custom button style, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=337"
  },
  {
    "text": "here, we need to add the .hoverEffect modifier ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=339"
  },
  {
    "text": "to add hover effects to the button with custom styling. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=342"
  },
  {
    "text": "Many apps have fun and custom interfaces. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=346"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this example of a beekeeping app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=349"
  },
  {
    "text": "buttons are honeycombs, where each honeycomb cell ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=352"
  },
  {
    "text": "is its own tap target. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=355"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apps implementing custom shape buttons will need to inform ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=358"
  },
  {
    "text": "the system how to render their hover effects. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=362"
  },
  {
    "text": "Frame width here is larger than the area the shape occupies, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=365"
  },
  {
    "text": "so the default system-provided hover effect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=369"
  },
  {
    "text": "covers the entire button frame, unbounded to shape. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=371"
  },
  {
    "text": "By passing a custom shape to the .contentShape modifier, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=377"
  },
  {
    "text": "hover effects will trim to the button's bounds. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=380"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's add that here. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=384"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now it is perfect, because when people look ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=386"
  },
  {
    "text": "at individual buttons, the hover effect is trimmed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=388"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the geometry of the button's shape. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=391"
  },
  {
    "text": "System controls that are disabled due to app state ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=394"
  },
  {
    "text": "automatically do not get hover effects. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=397"
  },
  {
    "text": "If apps want to de-emphasize specific interface elements, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=400"
  },
  {
    "text": "they can opt out individual items. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=403"
  },
  {
    "text": "People expect hover effects to be apparent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=406"
  },
  {
    "text": "and consistent across the system, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=408"
  },
  {
    "text": "so they should be turned off sparingly. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=410"
  },
  {
    "text": "The system accepts a maximum of two simultaneous inputs ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=413"
  },
  {
    "text": "since each hand is a distinct touch. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=417"
  },
  {
    "text": "Custom gesture recognizers are also supported, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=420"
  },
  {
    "text": "but you may need to update them to run smoothly ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=423"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the natural input expectations. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=425"
  },
  {
    "text": "Games, or other apps that need rapid or simultaneous input, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=428"
  },
  {
    "text": "need to support game controllers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=432"
  },
  {
    "text": "iPad and iPhone apps have long been able to indicate support ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=435"
  },
  {
    "text": "for game controllers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=438"
  },
  {
    "text": "On this platform, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=439"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's even more critical for additional input methods. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=440"
  },
  {
    "text": "By including GCSupports ControllerUserInteraction ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=445"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Info.plist and adding Game controller capability, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=449"
  },
  {
    "text": "it adds a badge to the app's product page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=452"
  },
  {
    "text": "This improves communication with people using App Store ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=455"
  },
  {
    "text": "to find games, and makes the availability ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=458"
  },
  {
    "text": "of game controllers even more evident across all platforms. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=461"
  },
  {
    "text": "For information about game controllers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=466"
  },
  {
    "text": "and games on App Store, watch the videos ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=468"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Advancements in Game Controllers\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=470"
  },
  {
    "text": "and \"Build great games for spatial computing.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=472"
  },
  {
    "text": "iPad and iPhone apps running on this platform ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=475"
  },
  {
    "text": "match their iPad light-mode appearance. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=478"
  },
  {
    "text": "In most cases, that looks great. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=481"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're using system standard controls, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=483"
  },
  {
    "text": "layouts, and colors, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "there's no new work for you here. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=487"
  },
  {
    "text": "The system optimizes rendering, using dynamic content scaling ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=490"
  },
  {
    "text": "so all images and text are always sharp ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=494"
  },
  {
    "text": "at any angle, from any distance. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=497"
  },
  {
    "text": "To provide the best experience, use vector-based content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=500"
  },
  {
    "text": "Prompts on iPad and iPhone are presented modally, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=506"
  },
  {
    "text": "so the prompt must be interacted with before continuing. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=509"
  },
  {
    "text": "On this new platform, prompts do not present modally. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=512"
  },
  {
    "text": "Prompts such as asking for location permission, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=517"
  },
  {
    "text": "Sign in with Apple, or OAuth, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=519"
  },
  {
    "text": "do not require handling before continuing. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=521"
  },
  {
    "text": "These interfaces create their own chrome ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=525"
  },
  {
    "text": "and windowed experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=527"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apps should be aware and handle cases where they get the prompt, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=529"
  },
  {
    "text": "but may not get immediate cancelled or success call backs. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=532"
  },
  {
    "text": "People capturing, sharing, and posting content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=537"
  },
  {
    "text": "is a great way to express themselves. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=540"
  },
  {
    "text": "On this platform, there are some differences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=543"
  },
  {
    "text": "apps should be aware of. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=545"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are multiple external and internal facing cameras. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=547"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, many of these cameras are not available for app use. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=551"
  },
  {
    "text": "It is critical to use discovery sessions to detect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=555"
  },
  {
    "text": "which cameras and microphones are available for use. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=558"
  },
  {
    "text": "To ensure apps have an excellent capture experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=563"
  },
  {
    "text": "use AVCaptureDevice discovery session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=566"
  },
  {
    "text": "to confirm hardware availability. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=568"
  },
  {
    "text": "Additionally, similar to other platforms, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=571"
  },
  {
    "text": "requesting permission before use is required. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=574"
  },
  {
    "text": "Lastly, generalize your authorization prompt string ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=578"
  },
  {
    "text": "to inform people of use, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=580"
  },
  {
    "text": "without mentioning specific hardware or software versions.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=582"
  },
  {
    "text": "When apps request camera and microphone availability, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=588"
  },
  {
    "text": "expect different values to be returned than iPad and iPhone. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=591"
  },
  {
    "text": "When querying microphone, apps will receive ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=595"
  },
  {
    "text": "a single .front location microphone. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=597"
  },
  {
    "text": "When querying camera, apps will find two cameras. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=600"
  },
  {
    "text": "The .back camera returns a black camera frame ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=604"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a no camera glyph. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=606"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is a nonfunctional camera to support apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=609"
  },
  {
    "text": "that assume back camera availability. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=611"
  },
  {
    "text": "When querying for front camera, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=614"
  },
  {
    "text": "apps find a single composite camera. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=616"
  },
  {
    "text": "If no spatial persona is found on a device, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=619"
  },
  {
    "text": "then no camera frames will return to apps. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=622"
  },
  {
    "text": "AVRoutePickerView and Picture in Picture ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=628"
  },
  {
    "text": "are unavailable on this platform, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=630"
  },
  {
    "text": "which has been reflected in system-provided players. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=632"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apps that implement custom players need to check ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=636"
  },
  {
    "text": "both availabilities before showing these controls. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=638"
  },
  {
    "text": "Lastly, this platform locks once removed. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=642"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apps that utilize background audio ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=645"
  },
  {
    "text": "should consider this difference, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=646"
  },
  {
    "text": "as they will no longer get this background mode ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=648"
  },
  {
    "text": "when the device is locked, and will be fully suspended. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=650"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apps that import media should consider alternative sources ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=655"
  },
  {
    "text": "when capture hardware isn't available. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=658"
  },
  {
    "text": "Options such as iCloud or content pickers, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=661"
  },
  {
    "text": "like document or photo picker, are excellent alternatives. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=663"
  },
  {
    "text": "Additionally, apps that use VisionKit's ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=669"
  },
  {
    "text": "VNDocumentCameraViewController will automatically capture ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=671"
  },
  {
    "text": "with Continuity Camera on a nearby device. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=675"
  },
  {
    "text": "These alternatives bring even more media-import options ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=678"
  },
  {
    "text": "to existing iPad and iPhone apps. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=681"
  },
  {
    "text": "iPad and iPhone apps run great on this new platform. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=685"
  },
  {
    "text": "Make sure hover effects are added ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=689"
  },
  {
    "text": "to all your interactive controls. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=690"
  },
  {
    "text": "For games, add controller support to ensure players ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=692"
  },
  {
    "text": "continue to have a great experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=695"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, review your assumptions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=698"
  },
  {
    "text": "about camera and microphone presence ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=700"
  },
  {
    "text": "by checking for availability before use. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=702"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now you know how to optimize iPad and iPhone apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=706"
  },
  {
    "text": "for this new platform. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=709"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm looking forward to using your apps in the shared space. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=711"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10094/?time=715"
  }
]